data.description: Charming 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Home with large front porch. The home's interior radiates warmth, making it an inviting haven.  A breakfast bars adds a cozy touch. From the dinning area French doors lead to the large covered back porch.   There is also a  Workshop with extra parking.    Additionally, a separate area is available for an RV or mobile home.  Complete with 2nd SEPTIC, 2nd WELL, and 2nd Electric Meter and separate Driveway. This versatile setup caters to both comfort and potential investment and income-generating possibilities.                                 THIS HOME SITS ON 4 ACRES  - secluded from the street by towering trees.                                     NO RESTRICTIONS - NO HOA FEES.             ENDLESS POSSIBILITIES !!!
